content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 800.24 - No parking on wharfs

State Regulations

It shall be unlawful for any person to leave any animal, automobile or other vehicle upon any wharf or portion of any wharf under the
control and management of the commission. Notes
